  "description": "A nighttime long exposure shot featuring a brightly lit suspension bridge stretching across a dark body of water. The bridge is illuminated with a series of orange and white lights that create a linear pattern across the water. The supports of the bridge are also lit, emphasizing its structure. The surrounding water reflects the lights, creating a shimmering effect.  Dark silhouettes of landmasses and vegetation frame the image on either side, creating a natural vignette. The sky is a deep, dark blue, indicating that it's late at night or early morning.",
